            markup: True
            text: "\n" "\n" "Examples of Phishing Emails will be shown." "\n" "\n" "Your job is to find obvious or subtle signs that giveaway something phishy is going on..." "\n" "\n" "A green tick will show up if a telltale sign is found"
            text: "\n" "\n" "Typical signs to look out for can be obvious but some can be hard to spot so try to look out for:" "\n" "\n" "\n" "[color=#FFFFFF]>""[color=#EE1414]   Suspicious links" "\n" "\n""[color=#FFFFFF]>" "[color=#EE1414]   Grammatical and or spelling errors" "\n" "\n" "[color=#FFFFFF]>""[color=#EE1414]   Was the message sent from a public domain name and or is the domain name spelt correctly."
            pos_hint: {'center_x': 0.75, 'center_y': 0.8}
            font_size: 22
        Label:
            text: "Click on all signs that you find and the next level will start" "\n" "\n" "Each level gets more difficult with the signs being harder to spot so keep your eyes peeled"
            pos_hint: {'center_x': 0.3, 'center_y': 0.2}
            font_size: 22

